works.description:
Going with the tradition of the last 8  
years, Audi has created a limited edition Chrome Audi R8, which will be  
auctioned at the Tie & Tierra dinner ball for the Elton John Aids  
Foundation (EJAF). Conceptualized and designed by the famous Damien Hirst,
 
this limited edition version of the Audi sports car is expected to be  
centre of attention at the event, and command a premium price like the
pink  
Audi A1 did last year.
